      <title>南非计划将 270 亿美元应急基金的一半用于削减债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/s-africa-eyes-half-of-27-billion-contingency-funds-to-cut-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国家财政部正在考虑提取央行持有的 4970 亿兰特（273 亿美元）应急储备中的一半，以帮助减轻政府债务负担或为公共部门工资提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/s-africa-eyes-half-of-27-billion-contingency-funds-to-cut-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 08:42:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧尔班敦促欧盟为匈牙利提供资金以换取乌克兰援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/orban-presses-for-hungary-s-eu-funds-in-return-for-ukraine-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·欧尔班周五表示，在欧盟支付从匈牙利扣留的所有资金之前，布达佩斯政府不会支持欧盟对乌克兰的新援助计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/orban-presses-for-hungary-s-eu-funds-in-return-for-ukraine-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 07:24:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国家电视台称，枪手在伊朗警察局袭击中杀死 11 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-15/urgent-gunmen-kill-11-people-injure-several-others-in-an-attack-on-a-police-station-in-iran-state-tv-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉伯联合酋长国迪拜（美联社）——国家电视台周五称，伊朗东南部一处警察局夜间遭到袭击，疑似分离主义组织成员造成 11 人死亡、数人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-15/urgent-gunmen-kill-11-people-injure-several-others-in-an-attack-on-a-police-station-in-iran-state-tv-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 06:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
