      <title>Milei 经济主管称阿根廷仍计划美元化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/argentina-still-plans-to-dollarize-milei-s-economy-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济部长表示，作为第一轮休克疗法的一部分，阿根廷比索大幅贬值后，总统哈维尔·米莱仍打算最终废除阿根廷比索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/argentina-still-plans-to-dollarize-milei-s-economy-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 02:56:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉和圭亚那同意在谈判继续期间不使用武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/venezuela-guyana-agree-not-to-use-arms-while-talks-continue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉和圭亚那在第一次会议上同意不对对方使用武器，以缓解有争议的埃塞奎博领土的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/venezuela-guyana-agree-not-to-use-arms-while-talks-continue</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 02:06:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院通过允许豁免的筹码，并将法案送交众议院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/senate-passes-chips-permitting-exemption-sending-bill-to-house</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议院批准了一项免除半导体项目联邦环境许可的法案，并将该措施提交众议院，旨在加快美国芯片行业的发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/senate-passes-chips-permitting-exemption-sending-bill-to-house</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 23:46:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟在就入盟谈判达成一致后未能支持乌克兰援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/eu-leaders-agree-to-membership-talks-with-kyiv-in-historic-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟领导人未能就针对乌克兰的新财政援助方案达成一致，将辩论推迟到明年初，欧盟正在努力应对西方支持动摇的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/eu-leaders-agree-to-membership-talks-with-kyiv-in-historic-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 17:32:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
